.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-6-2::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, broccoli, cherry, spinach
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, coffee, water, cola
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, punk, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, swimming, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is swimming is the person eating broccoli##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 4. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
 6. the person drinking fanta is between the fan blues and the person eating artichoke##2
 7. the fan blues is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 8. the fan soul is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person drinking cola is on the left of the fan hip-hop##1
10. the person who's sport is cricket is the person drinking cola##1
11. the person eating cherry is in an odd position##4
12. the fan blues is not the person who's sport is swimming##6
13. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the fan blues##1
14. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the fan punk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Food          | cherry    | artichoke | broccoli | spinach       |
| Hobby         | cola | coffee   | fanta  | water       |
| Music-Genre   | soul      | hip-hop   | punk     | blues         |
| Sport         | cricket   | cycling   | swimming | weightlifting |

